  "texts": [
    "7 An additional advantage is that we enjoy unfettered access to the original raw materials and results.",
    "In previous studies of this kind, the authors must do their best to faithfully adhere to the original study designs.",
    "In our setting, we can be confident to compare results like-for-like, and we can also introduce extensions that are still true to the model at hand.",
    "8 We verify this by asking GPT-4 to describe the experiment in Hoelzemann et al. (2024).",
    "The answers were nonsensical and largely hallucinated."
